DisclaimersData.ImportantInfoDisclaimer:
Important information

Portfolio can help you have a complete view of your wealth, integrating your banking and wealth management experience.

Information from products you hold with the Commonwealth Bank Group (Group) and information you may have provided in past product applications is automatically displayed. Some information you may have provided in past product applications may no longer be current. Except for actual account balances you can update or remove any of this information. Simply add anything else that you own or owe to get an estimate of your net worth.

Please note that some accounts and products, including Travel Money Card, Margin Loan, Foreign Currency accounts, Business Transaction and Savings accounts, and Bankwest products won’t be included in your portfolio view. You can choose to add them yourself, but the balances won't be updated automatically.
